meaning_str.bing:
n. 十二；十二岁；十二点钟；十二个东西[人]
num. 十二
网络. 第十二；十二匹；序数词

十二；十二岁；十二点钟；十二个东西[人]

十二；十二个（人或物）；十二岁；十二点钟；[宗]（耶稣的）十二门徒；十二音；十二进制；十二个单位一组；（指服装尺码）十二号

1.en: Kurt made his way to the twelve o'clock point, to Mendez, Mark, and Tom. Chief Mendez met him. The old man had never looked so grim.
1.cn: 库尔特前进到十二点方向，那里是门德兹，马克和汤姆。门德兹军士长跟他会合。这个老男人从来没看起来这么冷酷。

2.en: Then it was that Lottie knew why Bess had made no mention of her finery, or the shining room, or the twelve pound turkey.
2.cn: 那时珞蒂才明白何以碧丝都不提她美的服饰、漂亮的房间或者那只十二磅重的火鸡。

3.en: They had an arrangement by which he placed twelve dollars a week in her hands, out of which to pay current expenses.
3.cn: 他们约定，每星其他交到她手上12块钱，用作日常开支。

0.en: Eleven, twelve, thirteen ,fourteen, fifteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty.
0.cn: 十一，十二，十三，十四，十五，十六，十七，十八，十九，二十！

1.en: Twelve possible worlds, twelve Ranger launches carrying the bravest humans ever to live led by the remarkable Dr. Mann.
1.cn: 十二个可能的世界，十二架漫游者飞船，载着最勇敢的人，由了不起的Mann博士带队。

2.en: This is the ship that made the Kessel Run in 14 parsecs? Twelve! Fourteen.
2.cn: 这就是那艘只用十四秒差距完成科舍尔航程的飞船？十二秒！什么十四秒。

3.en: They've put potentially habitable worlds right within our reach. Twelve, in fact, from our initial probes.
3.cn: 他们将宜居的世界，放在了我们触手可及的地方，十二个，这是我们初步探查的结果。

4.en: What? The gun. But it works better if you flip the switch by your thumb. Careful. You've been asleep for almost twelve hours.
4.cn: 什么？那把枪。想要开枪得先把保险打开才行。小心点，你已经昏睡了十二个小时。

5.en: I am loving this country theme. This reminds me of when I worked for Newscenter Twelve in Tulsa, except no one here's bitter and drunk.
5.cn: 我超爱这个乡村主题！让我想起当初给塔尔萨市的十二新闻台工作的日子，除了这里没有刻薄的醉汉。

6.en: Kowloon's Walled City Park is a gateway into the world of classic Qing Dynasty design, and features statues of the twelve animals of the Chinese zodiac.
6.cn: 九龙寨城公园是进入清朝时期的时光门，里面不但有清朝的建筑设计，还有以中国十二生肖为题材而建的雕像。

8.en: No. No. I don't mean I see her as a twelve-year-old girl.
8.cn: 不，我不是把她当成12岁的小女孩。

9.en: Time. Yes, of course. I'll be at your door in twelve hours.
9.cn: 时间。当然。12小时内到你那边。

10.en: Okay, hey, that's okay with me. Two down and I have exactly twelve minutes.
10.cn: 我无所谓，已经搞定两个了，我还有整整12分钟。

11.en: And if you didn't visit them for twelve clicks, they would disappear forever.
11.cn: 如果你连续12次没有点击它们，它们就会永远消失。

12.en: So twelve to one lightning. Then one to two is blood, then fog and then monkeys.
12.cn: 12点到1点是闪电，1点到2点是血雨，然后是毒雾，再就是变种猴。

13.en: Did you at least win the contest? Two minutes, twelve pies and a part of one tin.
13.cn: 那你赢了没有？两分钟吃了12个外加一罐！

14.en: Well, it's my word against yours. 200 bucks a day, fluff, 365 days a year, since I was twelve.
14.cn: 空口无凭。小家伙，从我12岁起，每年365天，每天200块。

15.en: Oh, Dr. Siebert, twelve o'clock. Why's the president of the university slumming in the cafeteria?
15.cn: 12点方向，希伯特博士。为啥大学校长要来食堂里视察呢？

16.en: And it wasn't until you were twelve that you realized all the voices were in everyone else's head.
16.cn: 你到12岁了，这还未消停，然而你发现那些声音统统都是别人的脑里的想法。

17.en: The last one is at Fort Meade, behind three guarded gates and a twelve-inch steel wall. Shouldn't be a problem.
17.cn: 最后一个在米德堡，有三道大门把守，还有堵12英寸厚的钢墙。这不算事儿。

18.en: With a population of over twelve million people, the French capital is at the heart of the Ile-de-France region.
18.cn: 拥有超过一千两百万人口，是法国的首都，位在法兰西岛的心脏地带。

19.en: Oh man. I want that place so much. I was so sure that was gonna work. There's twelve bucks I'll never see again.
19.cn: 真是的，我好想要那层公寓，我还以为一定会成功，那12块钱算是一去不复返了。
